WEBVTT

00:00:29.240 --> 00:00:35.400
kako bih pokušao da shvatim ono
što neki zovu "put od škole do zatvora".

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:38.696
Kad pogledate ovakvu sliku,

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:41.280
maldih ljudi koje izučavam...

00:00:43.440 --> 00:00:44.856
možda vidite nevolje.

00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:49.056
Mislim, jedan od dečaka
drži flašu pića u ruci,

00:00:49.080 --> 00:00:51.216
ima 14 godina

00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:52.760
i školski je dan.

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.936
Drugi ljudi kad vide ovu sliku

00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.976
možda vide bande,

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.096
nasilnike, delinkvente -